{"tid":1055792,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[數學]人去到深夜,總係有好多奇怪諗法","createTime":"2019-03-10T18:19:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-10T19:22:04.000Z","uid":119994,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"30dfb5cc9509e7259b860a31e6461ed724ff2e6a","tid":1055792,"uid":119994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T18:19:07.000Z","msg":"我係度諗<br />\n究竟一個聯立方程，分別為degree m 同degree n<br />\n佢地既會唔會係exactly mn 個points（including complex roots）<br />\n以下為例子<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qWKWzzS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqWKWzzS.png&h=6481acba&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b4iXi1x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb4iXi1x.png&h=9edb6b0d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z1eGLGP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz1eGLGP.png&h=ee458ce0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n想證明又唔知點證明，想search 又唔知點search，想推翻又諗唔到實例（btw 我諗到唯一exceptional case 係兩條parallel lines，但如果include 到point of infinity 都仲會work）<br />\n有無連登數學家幫手？<br />\n<br />\nbtw 其他巴打對數學有d 古怪想法都可以share 下"},{"pid":"b3566c9d0fb2717ed4e78eb3082fb04a35eb3360","tid":1055792,"uid":159628,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T18:28:30.000Z","msg":"y=x^2<br />\ny=x^4"},{"pid":"dab41649ac392561c341de3b44799c1afdaf89ae","tid":1055792,"uid":34277,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T18:36:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/B%C3%A9zout%27s_theorem\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FB%25C3%25A9zout%2527s_theorem&d=NaAPOzxPFgptGlwmNixMN79ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=1da81394\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/B%C3%A9zout%27s_theorem</a><br />\n應該係呢個"},{"pid":"0dc343a53beab38c1a39b60815ec10993b6fc6a3","tid":1055792,"uid":119994,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dab41649ac392561c341de3b44799c1afdaf89a